{"tid":571126,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"俄羅斯二世祖想買兇殺父母攞遺產，點知...","createTime":"2018-02-24T11:22:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-24T11:49:16.000Z","uid":1886,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5b11c84aecd4a47c73d027b42c52e47bccad85a7","tid":571126,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T11:22:15.000Z","msg":"在俄羅斯一個富裕的家庭中，兒子因為覬覦家中豐厚的財產，竟然不惜上網尋找職業殺手來暗殺自己的父母與姊妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，只是沒想到自己的計畫卻早就被父母揭穿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，該名22歲疑犯數月來計劃暗殺其父母及姊姊，在網上搜尋殺人的方法。他曾嘗試在壺中落藥以毒殺父母，但其父卻察覺不妥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ；他之後打算在父母的座駕中打破溫度計，令二人水銀中毒，但因為膽怯而不敢親自落手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n他最後決定在網上尋找職業殺手，並將父母位於索契(Sochi)的豪宅平面圖，標示監視器位置，及如何避開守門犬，一一告訴「殺手」，還要求要看父母的屍體照為證，但他不知道自己聯絡的竟是臥底警探<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n疑犯的父母得悉兒子的可怖陰謀後，感到悲痛欲絕，決定與警方合作「詐死」把逆子繩之以法。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3130/d3130105.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3130%2Fd3130105.jpg&h=bbc6d110&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180223/bknint-20180223020043804-0223_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180223%2Fbknint-20180223020043804-0223_17011_001.html&d=uttWRRIPV6qOO%2Fem%2FmZFa5UWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=42c04b98\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180223/bknint-20180223020043804-0223_17011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"a6fc14e9130086a44be11345182840647e90b00c","tid":571126,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T11:23:11.000Z","msg":"臥底警員訛稱事成後，疑犯要求看父母的屍體照為證，警員便約他在一輛車上「收貨」。看到照片後，疑犯滿心歡喜，同意支付約41萬港元的報酬，臥底警員隨即顯露真面目。疑犯被捕後對犯行坦承不諱，還透露之前已兩度嘗試暗殺父母。他向警方供認，因為父母不給他錢而動殺機，又稱：「我已受夠他們了，他們根本不明白我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！」<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180223/photo/bknint-20180223020043804-0223_17011_001_02p.jpg?20180223131528\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180223%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20180223020043804-0223_17011_001_02p.jpg%3F20180223131528&h=92bc01b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">疑犯相約「殺手」在車上收相時被捕。</span></div>"},{"pid":"6f99bb2afa9c32762afdaa6d9d834c3fd1b0e953","tid":571126,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T11:24:04.000Z","msg":"雖然該對父母避過一劫，但兒子的所為已傷透他們的心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。據悉，疑犯的父親在索契辦學，有車有樓，及本來會落入兒子袋中的豐厚積蓄。疑犯一旦預謀買兇殺人罪成，或面臨判囚15年。"},{"pid":"b8d852682d0582be2fc91097ce68532dae80f362","tid":571126,"uid":27851,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T11:27:39.000Z","msg":"呢d人根本係蠢 思想諗埋一邊 遲早d錢實有得分"},{"pid":"651d62cf2126bdb832d4323ce5b43ccb390a95c2","tid":571126,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T11:34:25.000Z","msg":"好有勵志<br />\n敢做敢認  <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cff77da25a971f687e8939f5628029a7d28d8815","tid":571126,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T11:49:16.000Z","msg":"咁撚陰濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}